data.description: Welcome Home! Come take a look at this charming 3 bed / 2 full bath rambler while you still can. This is the first time this home has been on the market in almost 40 years and it's ready for new owners to build new memories. This fully-fenced home is situated on a level corner-lot with easy access to Hwy 512/I5, JBLM and only minutes to PLU. New hot water heater and furnace installed a few years ago. Extra storage shed in backyard. Make an appointment today!!
